metadata.name: Malicious Degenerates & Molesting Aliens
metadata.description:
NFT Digital flyer infused with underground post-psychedelia for a mixed sonic candyflipping experience by Katarshis.

Long before the industrialisation of trance & ambient electronica there were many years of chill out alienation & interpenetration, secret urban hideout raves & wet sensations of forest parties.

All transformed into slick stream of new sound which serves as a carrier wave conveying its true potential to those with compatible receivers implanted.

—

Comes with lossless copy of “Sonic Candyflipping” mix by Katarshis.
